message.content: cs.IT, cs.IT is the most likely category as the paper deals with information theory and entropy. Other possible categories could be cs.DS (discrete mathematics) as the paper deals with discrete random variables, cs.CC (computational complexity) as the paper discusses the complexity of certain inequalities, cs.SI (social and information networks) as entropy is often used in network analysis, and cs.LG (machine learning) as entropy is a commonly used measure in machine learning.
